commit.message:
Update libbacktrace config.sub from http://git.savannah.gnu.org/cgit/config.git

This is needed for it to compile on Redox.

Update libbacktrace config.sub from http://git.savannah.gnu.org/cgit/config.git

This is needed for it to compile on Redox.
